<span id="freeTextContainer14258401586794810154">Wonderful first hand account of all the daily details of Union army life in the Civil War. Extremely important for people to get the full picture of hardships and struggles that the soldiers faced every day. Does not cover warfare but discusses just about everything else. Truly helpful to fully envision the civil war experience. I highly recommend!</span>

